Title: Learn and Grow I: Seeds
Description:
Well, first things first! I'm going to need lots of help 'round here.

If we're going to be partners, you've got to learn how to harvest crops, and if you wanna harvest crops you gotta plant seeds!

Now it's my understanding that a mister, uh... Grainfell? No, that wasn't it... Greedfill? That doesn't sound right...

Greenfield! That's his name! He's the man to see for seeds.

Greenfield's got a stall over at Halfhill Market, directly southeast of here - go see him and pick up some vegetable seeds.
ObjectivesText: Speak with Merchant Greenfield at Halfhill Market and acquire a Packet of Green Cabbage Seeds.
CompletionText:
How'd it go, partner? Did you get those seeds from Groanfur?

Err... Greenfield?
RewardText:
He waved at me! And he gave you the first pack of seeds for free?

Well, what a nice guy!

You're doing a great job so far. Here's a little... seed money. Hah!
